Package: beltingSeq
Type: Package
Title: Processing and Visualization Tools for Microarray and RNA-seq Data
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: person("Marton Horvath", "marton.horvath@med.lu.se", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "marton.horvath@med.lu.se")
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for processing, analyzing, and visualizing
    microarray and RNA-seq data. Includes functions for data normalization,
    differential expression analysis, gene set enrichment analysis (GSEA),
    pathway clustering, and publication-ready visualizations.
